BO - Order details - Product block Details  Component : Core Status : Automated Automated on : 1.7.8.x, 1.7.7.x, 8.0.x, 8.1.x, 9.0.x Scenario : https://forge.prestashop.com/browse/TEST-737 Test : https://github.com/PrestaShop/PrestaShop/tree/develop/tests/UI/campaigns/functional/BO/02_orders/01_orders/viewAndEditOrder/02_productBlock.ts  Steps    Step Description Expected result     Go to BO -&gt; Orders -&gt; View last Order page The Order details page is displayed   Click on &ldquo;Delete&rdquo; button to remove the product and confirm the deletion An alert &ldquo;The product was successfully removed.&rdquo; is displayed and number products = 0   Click on Add a product The addProductTableRow is displayed   Search for standard simple product and click on it The &ldquo;Stock location&rdquo; value is correct and the &ldquo;Available&rdquo; quantity is correct   Click on &ldquo;Add&rdquo; A green alert &ldquo;The product was successfully added.&rdquo; is displayed and the new product is displayed in the list   Click on &ldquo;Add product&rdquo;, search the same product and click on &ldquo;Add&rdquo; A red alert &ldquo;Error! This product is already in your order, please edit the quantity instead.&rdquo; is displayed and the product cannot be added again   Click on the &ldquo;Cancel&rdquo; button The addProductTableRow is not displayed   Click on Add a product The addProductTableRow is displayed   Search for standard product with combinations and click on it The &ldquo;Stock location&rdquo; value is correct and the &ldquo;Available&rdquo; quantity is correct   Click on &ldquo;Add&rdquo; A green alert &ldquo;The product was successfully added.&rdquo; is displayed and the new product is displayed in the list   Click on Add a product The addProductTableRow is displayed   Search for virtual product and click on it The &ldquo;Stock location&rdquo; value is correct and the &ldquo;Available&rdquo; quantity is correct   Click on &ldquo;Add&rdquo; A green alert &ldquo;The product was successfully added.&rdquo; is displayed and the new product is displayed in the list   Click on Add a product The addProductTableRow is displayed   Search for pack product and click on it The &ldquo;Stock location&rdquo; value is correct and the &ldquo;Available&rdquo; quantity is correct   Click on &ldquo;Add&rdquo; A red alert &ldquo;{color:#FF0000}Error!{color}
{color:#FF0000}Minimum quantity of &ldquo;2&rdquo; must be added{color}&rdquo; is displayed   Increase quantity = minimal quantity The quantity is changed   Click on &ldquo;Add&rdquo; 1. A green alert &ldquo;The product was successfully added.&rdquo; is displayed and the new product is displayed in the list
2. The name is correct, the base price is correct, the quantity is correct, the Available is ok and the total is ok   Click on Add a product The addProductTableRow is displayed   Search for customized product (demo_14) and click on it The &ldquo;Stock location&rdquo; value is correct and the &ldquo;Available&rdquo; quantity is correct   Click on &ldquo;Add&rdquo; A green alert &ldquo;The product was successfully added.&rdquo; is displayed and the new product is displayed in the list   Click on Add a product The addProductTableRow is displayed   Search for an out of stock allowed product and click on it The &ldquo;Stock location&rdquo; value is correct and the &ldquo;Available&rdquo; quantity is correct   Click on &ldquo;Add&rdquo; A green alert &ldquo;The product was successfully added.&rdquo; is displayed and the new product is displayed in the list   Click on Add a product The addProductTableRow is displayed   Search for an out of stock not allowed product and click on it The &ldquo;Stock location&rdquo; value is correct, the &ldquo;Available&rdquo; quantity is correct and the &ldquo;Add&rdquo; button is disabled   Increase the quantity The &ldquo;Add&rdquo; button is still disabled   Click on &ldquo;Cancel&rdquo; button The addProductTableRow is not displayed   Click on Add a product The addProductTableRow is displayed   Search for a product with a specific price and click on it The base price and the total are correct   Click on Add a product The addProductTableRow is displayed   Search for a product with ecotax and click on it The base price and the total are correct   Click on Add a product The addProductTableRow is displayed   Search for a product with cart rule and click on it The base price and the total are correct Check that the discount line is well added   Click on &ldquo;Edit&rdquo; of the first product in the list The &ldquo;editProductRow&rdquo; is displayed   Edit the quantity, click on &ldquo;Save&rdquo; and confirm the modification The Quantity is